DataSourcePortable.Name: Fluxos Ativos
DataSourcePortable.Content: <DataSourceDefinition> <FromSql Alias="A" SelectCommand="SELECT count(A.ATIVO) as Ativos FROM FX_FLUXO A WHERE A.Ativo = 'S' group by A.Ativo" /> <Fields> <Field Alias="ATIVOS" From="A" Path="ATIVOS" /> </Fields> </DataSourceDefinition>
